{
  "stem": "5810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he had built a hiding place under a wooden stairway where there was a-- best way I can describe it, a false door that we could go into, I'd, I'd say, a space four feet by four feet, where my mother and I, whenever there was a search and there were many at that point, you know, banging on the door, searching for, for the son.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say in the period of time we were there, we probably had about 20 different searches.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not necessarily just because the son had escaped, it also happened that they were searching for Jews at that time also.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we must have had about 20 searches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after the third or fourth search, where we came so very close to being discovered under the stairway, because we heard a, a German-- one of the soldiers or Gestapo, I don't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't see their uniform-- banging on the stairway with his rifle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he could see-- hear the hollowness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I learned German by that time, and I understood very, very well what he had said.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Let's check underneath for any, any hiding places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I also remember him coming quite close, coming down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, well, that was it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a German officer screaming and yelling said, that's it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We've had it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Let's go on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he took him away from there, and we knew then that this wasn't the best place for us to hide.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Barniche, again-- we had an attic in in that house.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
